<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="off-adv">off <strong><em>adv</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /ɒf/    美 /ɔːf/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>离开：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>go / run off
走/跑开</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I must be off now.
我得走了。</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>离；距：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The city is 20 miles off.
那座城市在20英里以外。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>May Day is only a week off.
离五一劳动节只有一个星期了。</p></div>

<h4 id="3">3.★ <strong>脱离掉；去掉；减掉：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>take 10 percent off
削减10%</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The paint came off.
油漆脱落了。</p></div>

<h4 id="4">4.★ <strong>不工作；休息：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>take a day off
休假一天</p></div>

<h4 id="5">5.★ <strong>停止；延期：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>turn off the TV
关掉电视</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Don’t put off your work.
不要拖延工作。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">真题解析</h2>
<ol>
<li>She drove so fast at the turn that the car almost went <strong><em>_</em></strong>__ the road.  （2014 重庆改）  </li>
</ol>
<p>答案：
1. off  </p></div>